drawnet.lib.solvers
Class SolverFilter

java.lang.Object
  drawnet.lib.solvers.Solver
      drawnet.lib.solvers.SolverLauncher
          drawnet.lib.solvers.SolverFilter
Direct Known Subclasses:
SolverFilterAlgebra, SolverFilterAlgebra2, SolverFilterFT, SolverFilterFT2, SolverFilterGSPN, SolverFilterITPN, SolverFilterMGMTS, SolverFilterOsMoSys
public abstract class SolverFilter
extends SolverLauncher

This is an abstract class to derive solvers which use I/O filters. They normally launch an external program, needing formatted input files and generating output files. Every class which derives from this one gets a starting basic common interface and some utilities to develop its own solver.
